bilingual.source: Do you think this is fate or coincide?
bilingual.target: 你认为这是命运还是巧合？

bilingual.source: She will dree her fate with courage.
bilingual.target: 她将勇敢地承受自己的命运。

bilingual.source: The fate of all flesh is interconnected.
bilingual.target: 众生的命运是相互关联的。

bilingual.source: The jury decided the fate of the defendant.
bilingual.target: 陪审团决定了被告的命运。
你不能任意决定别人的命运。

bilingual.source: She strives to be the master of her fate.
bilingual.target: 她努力成为自己命运的主人翁。

bilingual.source: He left his fate in the hands of Providence.
bilingual.target: 他把自己的命运交给了天意。

bilingual.source: His fate depends on the court's adjudication.
bilingual.target: 他的命运取决于法庭的裁决。

bilingual.source: He believes that fate determines his destiny.
bilingual.target: 他相信天数决定了他的命运。

list.abstract: 《Fate》（フェイト，命运之夜），全称为《Fate/stay night》，是TYPE-MOON发售的文字冒险游戏系列，首作发布于2004年1月30日。 故事围绕着圣杯战争展开了一段惊心动魄的冒险，而在游戏初期的选择不同，后面的剧情也会出现极大改变的设定，也使得游戏的可玩性非常的高。
fate，英文单词。译作：命运，宿命；也可译作：注定。

yingyinNormal.en: So I'm just gonna leave it entirely up to the gods of fate.
Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to face your fate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以选择是否接受你的任务，那就是直面你的命运。

yingyinNormal.en: It was carrying a secret cargo, which would have changed our planets fate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其上装载了神秘货物，它能改变整个星球的命运。

yingyinNormal.en: And did my best to avoid the speccy-spotty fate that Helen had predicted for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽力避免海伦预言的成为青春痘四眼妹的命运。

yingyinNormal.en: He was meant to rendezvous with me here on Earth, before fate waylaid us both.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在命运将我们都打败之前他本该和我在地球会合。

yingyinNormal.en: However, the components of the universe can still affect its eventual fate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然而组成宇宙的各个部分同时也会影响其最终的命运。

yingyinNormal.en: The fate of the country will be decided tonight and I can't be seen at your side.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今晚是决定这个国家的命运的时候，我无法抽空去见你。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, believe it or not, the fate of the entire damn human race might depend on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，不管你信不信，整个人类的命运可全靠它了。

yingyinNormal.en: The film Interstellar deals with the quest for new worlds and the fate of humanity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电影《星际穿越》讲述的是对新世界和人类命运的探索。

yingyinNormal.en: Why? For what? Why do you walk on the wire? Why do you tempt fate? Why do you risk death?
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么？你为什么要走钢索？为什么要挑战命运？为什么冒险送死？

yingyinNormal.en: And now I see the fate of the world hangs on idiots like me. And that, sir, is sort of terrifying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可现在，我意识到全世界的命运掌握在我这样的白痴手里，这件事，先生，让我有些害怕。

yingyinNormal.en: Silence. I assure you that were you in Slytherin, and your fate rested with me the both of you would be on the train home tonight. As it is...
yingyinNormal.zh: 住口。我向你们保证，如果你们是史莱哲林的学生，而我有权力决定你们的命运时，你们两个，保证今晚就得搭列车回家。而且……
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: And suffered the same fate. It's a disappointing end to her story, isn't it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 结果落得相同的下场，真是个令人遗憾的结局，对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Have you made your decision regarding the fate of your father and uncle? No, Lord Kublai.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你决定了吗？如何处置你父亲和你叔叔？还没有，忽必烈大汗。

yingyinNormal.en: So you see, you can't quit. The fate of Bikini Bottom rests in your hands. But we're just…
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们看，你们不能退出。比基尼岛的未来就在你们手中。但是，但是我们只是……

yingyinNormal.en: And anyone who stands in our way will suffer the same fate as these men you see before you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 任何阻挡我们的人类，下场都会和你们面前看到的这些人一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Two, you let me walk away to an uncertain fate. You use the disk as bait to trap Lane. But some part of you suspect you've met your match.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第二，你放我走，让我去面对未知的一切，接着用这个硬盘去引诱莱恩上钩，但是你内心深处又害怕棋逢敌手。

yingyinNormal.en: While it might sound depressing living in a universe that will end its lifetime cold and devoid of life, the end fate of our universe actually has a beautiful symmetry to its hot, fiery beginning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管这听起来让人觉得生活在宇宙之中十分沮丧，因为它将在寒冷和了无生气中走向灭亡，但宇宙最终冰冷的消亡却完美地与其火热的发端相称。

word_usage.usage:
作名词表示“命运”
fate多指不好的命运，带有不可避免的意味。
destiny指将来一定会发生在某人身上的事情，尤指无法改变或控制的事。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 意为“命运、宿命”，带有神化或迷信色彩，使人有畏惧和无可奈何之感。
意为“运气、好运”，常指决定或影响人们生活的命运和机会。
常指“最终的、毁灭性或灾难性的命运”。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 她的父亲Robin Williams斯于2014年去世，他渴望避免同样的命运。
